    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The idea was that `label` could be a React node, while `key` would necessarily be a string, in cases where you want your label to contain more complex markup.\n\nI added a filter to search so that the `ClearAll` component could also clear the search, while the `CurrentFilters` clear all button would clear everything but the search. I believe this behavior is consistent with instantsearch v1?\n",
